                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "T'a prouvé la Divinité.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Ton âme, éclairée et profonde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Franchissant les bornes du monde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "S'élance au sein de son auteur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Tu parais son plus bel ouvrage ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et tu lui rends un digne hommage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Exempt de faiblesse et d'erreur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Charmante et sublime Émilie\nAmante de la Vérité,\nTa solide philosophie\nT'a prouvé la Divinité.\nTon âme, éclairée et profonde,\nFranchissant les bornes du monde,\nS'élance au sein de son auteur.\nTu parais son plus bel ouvrage ;\nEt tu lui rends un digne hommage,\nExempt de faiblesse et d'erreur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Mais si les traits de l'Athéisme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Sont repoussés par ta raison,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "De la coupe du Fanatisme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Ta main renverse le poison :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Tu sers la justice éternelle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Sans l'âcreté de ce faux zèle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "De tant de dévots malfaisants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Tel qu'un sujet sincère et juste",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Sait approcher d'un trône auguste",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Sans les vices des courtisans.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais si les traits de l'Athéisme\nSont repoussés par ta raison,\nDe la coupe du Fanatisme\nTa main renverse le poison :\nTu sers la justice éternelle,\nSans l'âcreté de ce faux zèle\nDe tant de dévots malfaisants,\nTel qu'un sujet sincère et juste\nSait approcher d'un trône auguste\nSans les vices des courtisans."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Ce Fanatisme sacrilège",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Est sorti du sein des autels ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Il les profane, il les assiège,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Il en écarte les mortels.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "O Religion bienfaisante,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Ce farouche ennemi se vante",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "D'être né dans ton chaste flanc !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Mère tendre, mère adorable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Croira-t-on qu'un fils si coupable",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Ait été formé de ton sang ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ce Fanatisme sacrilège\nEst sorti du sein des autels ;\nIl les profane, il les assiège,\nIl en écarte les mortels.\nO Religion bienfaisante,\nCe farouche ennemi se vante\nD'être né dans ton chaste flanc !\nMère tendre, mère adorable,\nCroira-t-on qu'un fils si coupable\nAit été formé de ton sang ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "On a vu souvent des athées",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Estimables dans leurs erreurs ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Leurs opinions infectées",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "N'avaient point corrompu leurs mœurs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Spinosa fut toujours fidèle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "A la loi pure et naturelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Du Dieu qu'il avait combattu ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Et ce Desbarreaux qu'on outrage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "S'il n'eut pas les clartés du sage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "En eut le cœur et la vertu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "On a vu souvent des athées\nEstimables dans leurs erreurs ;\nLeurs opinions infectées\nN'avaient point corrompu leurs mœurs.\nSpinosa fut toujours fidèle\nA la loi pure et naturelle\nDu Dieu qu'il avait combattu ;\nEt ce Desbarreaux qu'on outrage,\nS'il n'eut pas les clartés du sage,\nEn eut le cœur et la vertu."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Je sentirais quelque indulgence",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Pour un aveugle audacieux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Qui nierait l'utile existence",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "De l'astre qui brille à mes yeux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Ignorer ton être suprême,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Grand Dieu ! c'est un moindre blasphème,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Et moins digne de ton courroux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Que de te croire impitoyable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "De nos malheurs insatiable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Jaloux, injuste comme nous.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je sentirais quelque indulgence\nPour un aveugle audacieux\nQui nierait l'utile existence\nDe l'astre qui brille à mes yeux.\nIgnorer ton être suprême,\nGrand Dieu ! c'est un moindre blasphème,\nEt moins digne de ton courroux,\nQue de te croire impitoyable,\nDe nos malheurs insatiable,\nJaloux, injuste comme nous."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Lorsqu'un dévot atrabilaire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Nourri de superstition,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "A, par cette affreuse chimère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Corrompu sa religion,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Le voilà stupide et farouche ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Le fiel découle de sa bouche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Le Fanatisme arme son bras ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Et, dans sa piété profonde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Sa rage immolerait le monde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "A son Dieu, qu'il ne connaît pas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Lorsqu'un dévot atrabilaire,\nNourri de superstition,\nA, par cette affreuse chimère,\nCorrompu sa religion,\nLe voilà stupide et farouche ;\nLe fiel découle de sa bouche,\nLe Fanatisme arme son bras ;\nEt, dans sa piété profonde,\nSa rage immolerait le monde\nA son Dieu, qu'il ne connaît pas."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Ce sénat proscrit dans la France,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Cette infâme Inquisition,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Ce tribunal où l'ignorance",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Traîna si souvent la raison ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Ces Midas en mitre, en soutane,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Au philosophe de Toscane",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Sans rougir ont donné des fers.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Aux pieds de leur troupe aveuglée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Abjurez, sage Galilée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Le système de l'univers.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ce sénat proscrit dans la France,\nCette infâme Inquisition,\nCe tribunal où l'ignorance\nTraîna si souvent la raison ;\nCes Midas en mitre, en soutane,\nAu philosophe de Toscane\nSans rougir ont donné des fers.\nAux pieds de leur troupe aveuglée,\nAbjurez, sage Galilée,\nLe système de l'univers."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Écoutez ce signal terrible",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Qu'on vient de donner dans Paris ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Regardez ce carnage horrible,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Entendez ces lugubres cris ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Le frère est teint du sang du frère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Le fils assassine son père,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "La femme égorge son époux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Leurs bras sont armés par des prêtres.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "O ciel ! sont-ce là les ancêtres",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "De ce peuple léger et doux ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Écoutez ce signal terrible\nQu'on vient de donner dans Paris ;\nRegardez ce carnage horrible,\nEntendez ces lugubres cris ;\nLe frère est teint du sang du frère,\nLe fils assassine son père,\nLa femme égorge son époux ;\nLeurs bras sont armés par des prêtres.\nO ciel ! sont-ce là les ancêtres\nDe ce peuple léger et doux ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Jansénistes et molinistes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "Vous qui combattez aujourd'hui",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Avec les raisons des sophistes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "Leurs traits, leur bile, et leur ennui,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "Tremblez qu'enfin votre querelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "Dans vos murs un jour ne rappelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 87,
                    "line_text": "Ces temps de vertige et d'horreur ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 88,
                    "line_text": "Craignez ce zèle qui vous presse :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 89,
                    "line_text": "On ne sent pas dans son ivresse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 90,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'où peut aller sa fureur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Jansénistes et molinistes,\nVous qui combattez aujourd'hui\nAvec les raisons des sophistes,\nLeurs traits, leur bile, et leur ennui,\nTremblez qu'enfin votre querelle\nDans vos murs un jour ne rappelle\nCes temps de vertige et d'horreur ;\nCraignez ce zèle qui vous presse :\nOn ne sent pas dans son ivresse\nJusqu'où peut aller sa fureur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 91,
                    "line_text": "Malheureux, voulez-vous entendre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 92,
                    "line_text": "La loi de la religion ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 93,
                    "line_text": "Dans Marseille il fallait l'apprendre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 94,
                    "line_text": "Au sein de la contagion,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
